General.Name: Hubei Century Network Technology Co Ltd
General.Description: Hubei Century Network Technology Inc. operates an online entertainment platform in China and internationally. The company provides Internet games under the Life and Death Fighting 5, Three Kingdoms 11, The Age of Voyage 4, Dynasty Warriors 6, and Dynasty Warriors 8 names. It also offers IP introduction and authorization, IP game supervision, and other services; and deploy cloud acceleration services. In addition, the company's platform products comprise cloud service scenarios, online entertainment scenarios, and offline venue scenarios. Hubei Century Network Technology Inc. was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Wuhan, China.
